FBIS4-61805 "drsov090_t_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-090 Daily Report 9 May 1994 BALTIC STATES Estonia Laar Calls for Clarification of Grachev Remarks Laar Calls for Clarification of Grachev Remarks LD0905190894 Tallinn Radio Tallinn Network in Estonian 1700 GMT 9 May 94 LD0905190894 Tallinn Radio Tallinn Network Estonian BFN [Text] Estonian Prime Minister Mart Laar has instructed the Foreign Ministry to demand from the Russian Foreign Ministry clarification concerning Defense Minister Pavel Grachev's 6 May anti-Estonian statement. The prime minister hopes that the Russian defense minister's statement represents his personal stance and not the official standpoint of Russia. The Estonian prime minister expressed hope that the Russian Foreign Ministry will refute Grachev's irresponsible and (?tension-creating) statement. In Mart Laar's opinion, the statement by the Russian minister of defense may increase (?a dangerous threat) to Estonian independence and sovereignty.
